/Preferences titles-descriptions
App intro Launch the app intro,displayed first time you started up Kokotime. Installed version Check for updates Checking You are running the latest version ! Direct play in landscape When your device is in landscape mode the app will not show a play options menu but will directly play the requested video using the in app player.
Auto play next episode When using a series addon, the video player or cast remote will attempt to play the next episode automatically at the end of the current one.
Display featured movies section Displays the featured movies section when opening an addon if the addon provides a featured section.
Display currently watching movies section Displays the currently watching movies section when you open a movies addon.
Display currently watching series section Displays the currently watching episode of a series when you open a series addon.
Display featured series section Displays the featured series section when you open an addon, this is possible only if the addon provides featured content.
Change the linked addon repository The addon store url is the url the addon manager uses to request available addons, addon updates etc.
Play settings Movie addons settings Series addons settings Local Library Force library indexation Here you can force a library indexation when the app doesn\'t automatically do it. The app usually does this automatically when new files are introduced to the system.
